</p><a href="https://religionnews.com/2020/07/09/jehovahs-witnesses-to-move-global-conventions-online-amid-covid19-pandemic-christensen/" class="ctf-twitter-card ctf-tc-type-summary_large_image" target="_blank"><div class="ctf-tc-summary-info"><p class="ctf-tc-heading">Jehovah&#8217;s Witnesses move global conventions online amid COVID-19 pandemic</p><p class="ctf-tc-desc">(RNS) —  Jehovah&#039;s Witnesses have moved their large-scale conventions, which have been held every year since 1897, online due to COVID-19.</p><p class="ctf-tc-url">religionnews.com</p></div></a></div><div class="ctf-tweet-actions"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?in_reply_to=1281709788297134081&related=RNS" class="ctf-reply" target="_blank" style=""><i class="fa fa-reply"></i><span class="ctf-screenreader">Reply on Twitter</span></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/retweet?tweet_id=1281709788297134081&related=RNS" class="ctf-retweet" target="_blank" style=""><i class="fa fa-retweet"></i><span class="ctf-screenreader">Retweet on Twitter</span><span class="ctf-action-count ctf-retweet-count">6</span></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/like?tweet_id=1281709788297134081&related=RNS" class="ctf-like" target="_blank" style=""><i class="fa fa-heart"></i><span class="ctf-screenreader">Like on Twitter</span><span class="ctf-action-count ctf-favorite-count">2</span></a><a href="https://twitter.com/RNS/status/1281709788297134081" class="ctf-twitterlink" style="" target="_blank">Twitter</a></div></div><div class="ctf-item ctf-author-religioscope ctf-new ctf-retweet" id="ctf_1281713193941950465" style=""><div class="ctf-context"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=religioscope" target="_blank" class="ctf-retweet-icon"><i class="fa fa-retweet"></i><span class="ctf-screenreader">Retweet on Twitter</span></a><a href="https://twitter.com/religioscope" target="_blank" class="ctf-retweet-text" style="">Religioscope Retweeté</a></div><div class="ctf-author-box"><div class="ctf-au